title: Lindsay Rosner on Jobs Report, Fed Monetary Policy, Mortgages
description: Lindsay Rosner, head of multi-sector fixed income investing at Goldman Sachs Asset Management speaks with Scarlet Fu about the jobs report, Fed monetary policy and President Trump's mortgage bond announcement. (Source: Bloomberg)
